flowchart TD
    A[User Task] -->|task string| B[LearnKit.agent wrapper]
    B -->|prepare_run task| C[Classifier classify_task]
    C -->|ClassificationOutput domains/task_type| D[SemanticRetriever.retrieve]
    D -->|query/domain/scope| E[Backend search/hybrid_search]
    E -->|candidate MemoryRecords| F[MemoryRouter.route]
    F -->|top records bounded by count and token budget| G[determine_inference_mode]
    G -->|mode value| H[compose_context]
    H -->|_learnkit_context string| I[Wrapped agent function]
    I -->|system+user prompt| J[LLM Provider]
    J -->|response text| K[finalize_run]
    K -->|trajectory + response| L[Evaluator.evaluate_with_llm_judge]
    L -->|score/reasoning| M{score >= threshold}
    M -->|yes| N[MemoryDistiller.distill]
    N -->|skill/facts/failures/trace| O[memory_quality.decide_storage]
    M -->|no| P[MemoryDistiller.distill_failure]
    P -->|FailureRecord active| O
    O -->|store/reinforce/demote decisions| Q[Backend add/replace/update]
    Q -->|persisted records| R[(SQLite records + FTS + optional vec)]
    K -->|final response| S[Caller receives output]
